chunks.html_content:
Search for free by charity name, number, date of registration or by where the charity operates.

You can also view charities by:

  • income
  • income category
  • sector
  • top 10 by income, spending or other criteria

Charities won’t be in the register if they:

  • haven’t registered as they have an income below £5,000 or are ‘excepted’
  • are exempt from regulation by the Charity Commission
